{"tid":2112143,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【對沖人生】香港終極篇 資金人才撤 - 錢志健","createTime":"2020-07-17T05:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T06:48:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87c55857085034028748133840563233083ee35d","tid":2112143,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200717/DHRCBKDRVG7ZUVA5UART5DBKTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200717%2FDHRCBKDRVG7ZUVA5UART5DBKTI%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=1d88a8eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200717%2FDHRCBKDRVG7ZUVA5UART5DBKTI%2F&h=e5bb1f8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200717/DHRCBKDRVG7ZUVA5UART5DBKTI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【對沖人生】香港終極篇 資金人才撤 - 錢志健<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6DteUTbORhyqmWqacOXH3b5UIHQ=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MY7HSKLY3H7R2QKI3FCNOFLSNM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6DteUTbORhyqmWqacOXH3b5UIHQ%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMY7HSKLY3H7R2QKI3FCNOFLSNM.jpg&h=874a5972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港版國安法下，更大的清算可能是把幾個關鍵人物「祭旗」，資產隨時被凍結，在香港作投資，只是浪費時間。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普最終簽署了《香港自治法案》，也簽署行政命令，取消對香港的特殊待遇。美國商會也做了一項調查，受訪的機構當中，36%成員有意向把資金及業務撤出香港。在此一提，美國重炮手商務部長Wilbur Ross在國安法硬推前的一刻已提示，在港的美國公司要好好審視是否需要把亞洲總部撤離香港。《紐約時報》也在未來一年，會把三分一員工調去南韓首爾，投資銀行德銀DB的新任CEO將會長駐新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n對一般市民來說，美國取消對香港特區護照持有人的特殊待遇，確實「燒不到」太多中共官員。如何做到「真制裁」把香港價值出賣的官員，不少人拭目以待。在此領域，特朗普「留下一手」，聽說林鄭月娥、鄧炳強及韓正已在制裁名單內，中共政治攬炒，同時間譴責世界干預中國內政，香港難以有安寧。<br />\n<br />\n中國稱禁止官員拿外國護照。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關鍵人物隨時被祭旗<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。國家要錢，本應只需繳交15%香港個人入息稅，突然要多付30%的「差額」，而這個內地「稅網長臂」，已經延伸到全世界有分行的國企。<br />\n<br />\n最後，香港「被換血」，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n61萬人出嚟投票得來不易，我們未敢放棄。Free Hong Kong神話倒下前，由一班有心人作歷史見證，但要離開的，不要忘記我哋。<br />\n<br />\n錢志健<br />\n資深對沖基金經理<br />\nmailto:mdehedgecenter@gmail.com<br />\n本欄逢周五刊出"},{"pid":"ed1780d814173a1888ec521bd946998afe44a9ac","tid":2112143,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"睇錯車志健<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31afb6a99924a961c5af592dedd0f8be82eacdaa","tid":2112143,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18e005b54dd033dd3f27300f45feec0c0abf8558","tid":2112143,"uid":20362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:22:36.000Z","msg":"屌你以為brain <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b701ef8a10f5af104daeb4bbc09657dca5db0be","tid":2112143,"uid":59910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:47:33.000Z","msg":"成篇文好似冇乜實際內容，似呻多d...."},{"pid":"097c4561a4d055299f9bbe5b325446785c102a95","tid":2112143,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:48:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}